- Beat Drew Brees in New Orleans
- Beat Patrick Mahomes in Super Bowl

node.text:
This was one of many early mornings and long nights. We filmed this almost a year ago, and it brings back crazy memories. So grateful for our team for riding the journey with us! 

______________________

#Repost @elitemediaconcepts
・・・
What it took to create a one minute feature. 

Thanks to our client @demarcusware  and his team, @angelamariedaniel  @rlchap , for giving us creative freedom and trusting that we could have brought his vision to life. Thanks to the amazing dream team that pulled it off. 

Thanks to everyone who I know will support and follow @driventowin 

__________________
Team:
@ericamelissa_  @the_truth876 @davidherrera000 @tmproductions13  @thomasbiggars

node.text:
Today is my Grandma’s homegoing service😕. It’s hard to think about it as a celebration of life when she was the one who made it all happen. She made that starting 5 and each kid had at least 3 kids …and now their kids have at least 3 kids!!

Grandma, we celebrate you today for paving the way for the Ware’s. I thank you for keeping me on the right path and pulling me out of my darkest times. I thank you for the prayer time we had to make me a better man. Thank you for giving us just enough. Thank you for being “moms” when MY mom had to work 3 jobs. 

Thank you for that peanut butter and jelly sandwich we had everyday at midnight (she knew I wanted to gain weight). Thank you for being the matriarch of the family. Thank you for making me feel first and putting yourself second, so I could make a monumental change for the family. Your sacrifices will keep blessing the Ware’s forever.  I promise to make sure your sacrifices never go in vain and I will never forget why I smile so much!! 

Rest in Paradise 🙏🏾 
Willie Mae “Babe” Oliver Ware

node.text:
It’s easy to eat the cheese when the plate is full or the right things, moments, or circumstances have aligned. But don’t starve yourself of the appreciation prayer that got you there. Take the time in whatever moment you’re in - good or bad and decide to smile just for a moment. Tell yourself “I have arrived in happiness” or “I got this” or “I’m not alone.” Don’t be the one who smiles through your worst pains just to stop the tears from falling. Behind a smile, is a always a story you’ll never understand. 

P.S. My Grandma told me “Give a stranger one of your smiles. It might be the only sunshine they see all day.” Now I know where I got my smile from! Miss you🙏🏾

node.text:
🗣Freebie Alert!!! My birthday is tomorrow, but the celebration starts now! I’m gifting my fans and fitness junkies merch from my Fitness Brand @driventowin 💪🏾. The offer starts now and ends Sunday night at Midnight ⏰!! 

Happy Leo Season… the only thing better than #FREE, is living to see another FREE day!

All you have to do is (famous last words😝):
1. Download “D2W Fitness” (on either Apple or Android)
2. Pick your subscription option and select “start your free trial”
3. When your purchase goes through you will be prompted to enter your email
4. Tap submit to receive your code
5. Tag 3 friends who need fitness in their life or who need new workout gear 🤭

**If you feel like you did not receive your code and should have, please tap the settings icon on the top right and select “send feedback” and we will get it sorted out.

Now let’s crush the weekend 💪🏾.
